  "comment": "Решение:\nТ.к. \\((x^2-25)^2 \\geq 0\\) и \\((x^2+3x-10)^2 \\geq 0, \\Rightarrow (x^2-25)^2+(x^2+3x-10)^2\\geq 0\\) только когда\n\\(\\begin{cases}x^2-25=0 (1) \\\\x^2+3x-10=0 (2)\\end{cases}\\)\n\\((1) x^2-25=0\\)\n\\((x-5)(x+5)=0\\)\n\\((2) x^2+3x-10=0\\)\n\\(D=9+40=49\\)\n\\(x_1=\\cfrac{-3-7}{2}\\)\n\\(x_1=-5\\)\n\\(x_2=\\cfrac{-3+7}{2}\\)\n\\(x_2=2\\)\n\\(\\begin{cases}(x-5)(x+5)=0 \\\\x=-5; x=2\\end{cases}\\)\n\\(\\begin{cases}x=5; x=-5 \\\\x=2; x=-5\\end{cases}\\)\n\\(\\Rightarrow x=-5\\\\\\)\nОтвет:\\(-5\\)",
